content:
Install TB on the Mac and add the account that is on the Windows PC, as an IMAP account. If the account is also IMAP on the PC, mail will be synced between the two computers. If the PC account is POP, you probably want to switch it to IMAP.

https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/installing-thunderbird-on-mac
creator: sfhowes

content: Alt+V then select headers from the menu and select Normal. What you are seeing is ALL
